title: Secret Garden Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Italian, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Serves a wide range of international cuisines including Balanese and Japanese. Vegan choices include in-house-made organic and local miso, fresh fruit/veggie juices and smoothies, plus a raw food menu. Also has yoga lessons, music, retreating, chanting events. Free Wi-Fi.
